giant in November. Driving this decrease in shares of the tech</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1183284106/image_1183284106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743800-oracle-orcl-stock-q2-earnings-still-essential-for-agi", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 13:55:00"}, {"id": "4743801", "title": "Nongfu Spring: Improved Outlook For Water And Tea Businesses (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Row of assorted water bottles against the ocean\" data-id=\"112295204\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1126px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/112295204/image_112295204.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Henrik Sorensen/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <di