c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1449617186/image_1449617186.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Abstract Aerial Art</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Topline Summary and Update</h2> <p>Cardiff Oncology (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRDF\" title=\"Cardiff Oncology, Inc.\">CRDF</a></span>) has been a biotech of growing interest over the past few years, racing up and down as the fortunes of their PLK1 inhibitor onvansertib have risen and fallen. In particular, there</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1449617186/image_1449617186.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743799-cardiff-oncology-the-long-awaited-first-line-mcrc-data-are-here-but-the-work-is-just-beginning", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 13:38:41"}, {"id": "4743796", "title": "SSAB: Difficult To Forecast The Future In Steel, But Appealing Below 50 SEK", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1636870316/image_1636870316.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Borlange, Sweden\" data-id=\"1636870316\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1636870316/image_1636870316.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1636870316/image_1636870316.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1636870316/image_1636870316.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1636870316/image_163687031